flowchart TD

User[User Question]

User
   → APIGW[API Gateway]

APIGW
   → Lambda[Lambda Orchestrator]

Lambda
   → Session[DynamoDB Session Store]

Lambda
   → Catalog[Data Catalog Loader]

Catalog
   → Planner

Lambda
   → Planner[LLM Planner]

Planner
   → QuerySpec[QuerySpec JSON]

QuerySpec
   → Validator[QuerySpec Validator]

Validator
   → Resolver[Dataset Resolver]

Resolver
   → SQLBuilder[SQL Builder AST]

SQLBuilder
   → DB[(Aurora PostgreSQL)]

DB
   → Formatter[Response Formatter]

Formatter
   → Response[User Response]
